node.title: No, You Did Not!
node.description: After giving the early morning challenge to attendees at the GYCEurope Focus event in Leicester, UK, Sebastien Braxton then gives this as a follow up message. It's one thing to get up early in the mornings but what do we bring to God when we come to Him? in this sermon he shares how we can add purpose and meaning to the time we spend with God and exercise faith in Him.
